{"tid":589633,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】可恥！紅軍輸波加歷查向細路吐口水","createTime":"2018-03-12T03:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T13:05:48.000Z","uid":4661,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"435cab4dcf9d51032f5e7b1813849ee13597e3f4","tid":589633,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180312/photo/bkn-20180312090024297-0312_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180312092257\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180312%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180312090024297-0312_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180312092257&h=c961ca0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加歷查放飛劍：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2HlVC8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HlVC8s&d=uZa1rOfCoiDqybx2RrHmXwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=27af8202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2HlVC8s</a>　 <br />\n<br />\n可惡！利物浦日前喺英超輸畀死敵曼聯，「紅軍」名宿加歷查賽後竟然搵個細路女發脾氣，兜口兜面吐口水搞喊細路女！ <br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》報道，擔任《天空體育》評述嘅加歷查，賽後揸車離開嗰陣，突然聽到隔離車響銨，車上男子向加歷查挑釁：「2比1呀！加歷查2比1呀！」加歷查隨即打開車窗回應：「好嘅！」再吐口水還擊，而且口水兜面噴落男子個14歲囡囡臉上，片段內聽到囡囡投訴：「佢吐我口水呀！」男子就驚訝表示：「噢！加歷查向我個女吐口水，你好嘢！加歷查你好嘢！」 <br />\n<br />\n片段曝光後引嚟極大回響，《天空體育》已經傳召加歷查照肺，發言人表示：「呢個行為係不能接受，我哋會同加歷查研究點樣處理。」至於加歷查事後亦知衰，已聯絡細路女一家道歉，同時發出公開道歉聲明，似乎希望想保住隻飯碗。"},{"pid":"494607aa8749d9b454d230efb4bec256a8d891cc","tid":589633,"uid":8636,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"嘩 烏龍茶咁搞叫啲痢狗點拆呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ba2695c798959f7024f06b8b4f7ed17f1294a0","tid":589633,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"